Show HN: Offstage – A simpler, yet smarter, data analytics tool for creators
text:
Hey HN! I'd like to present our data analytics tool for creators. Understanding data is so important for creators and musicians but making sense of it can be really difficult and time consuming to do, so we wanted to make something better. Something simple and purpose-built.

The idea is simple: Connect the data sources used by musicians and creators (Eventbrite, Shopify, etc) into our tool, then ask questions using natural language in a Q&A interface to pull up answers to complex questions like "How many of my fans are based in LA and haven't bought merchandise from me yet?"

We're still very early on and we're focusing on getting feedback from creators, musicians, and anyone who could benefit from a "simpler" data tool. Would love feedback from this community!

Ask HN: Can you generate text in your dreams?
text:
I occasionally have lucid dreams or can remember dreams quite vividly. Something that I’ve noticed is that in my dreams I can’t generate text. It’s very reminiscent of the kind of text you see generated by AI.

Was just wondering if this is just me and everyone else is having great fun reading newspapers in their dreams…
